417
00:23:49,080 --> 00:23:50,080
And guess what?

418
00:23:50,080 --> 00:23:51,280
They didn't flex at the same time.

419
00:23:51,560 --> 00:23:52,600
What does that tell you?

420
00:23:52,680 --> 00:23:53,760
Their movements weren't in sync.

421
