461
00:25:36,320 --> 00:25:37,160
Right, what's the point?

462
00:25:37,160 --> 00:25:37,920
Wei!

463
00:25:37,960 --> 00:25:38,920
How many more days do we do this?

464
00:25:39,000 --> 00:25:39,880
Give us a straight answer.

465
00:25:40,200 --> 00:25:41,560
A straight answer, right?

466
00:25:41,560 --> 00:25:42,560
Yeah, give us a straight answer.

467
00:25:43,160 --> 00:25:44,520
If we can't form the Three-Zhang-Three,

468
00:25:45,000 --> 00:25:46,000
