469
00:25:46,000 --> 00:25:47,480
When are we finally going to make one?

470
00:25:47,480 --> 00:25:48,760
We can't keep dragging this out, right?

471
00:25:48,760 --> 00:25:50,000
Right, we can't keep dragging it out.

472
00:25:51,400 --> 00:25:52,200
You're asking me?

473
00:25:52,680 --> 00:25:53,520
I should be asking you lot!

474
00:25:53,760 --> 00:25:54,880
What's that supposed to mean?

475
00:25:55,320 --> 00:25:56,200
Can't form a single sheet,

476
00:25:56,200 --> 00:25:57,240
