495
00:26:23,160 --> 00:26:25,000
Wei Jianzhi runs a solo-slot.

496
00:26:25,280 --> 00:26:26,440
We're different.

497
00:26:26,720 --> 00:26:27,720
The moment I take time off,

498
00:26:28,200 --> 00:26:29,720
