And there's the drying and trimming crew too.

503
00:26:37,000 --> 00:26:39,440
Two forming, two drying, one trimming.

504
00:26:39,720 --> 00:26:41,240
We're one team.

505
00:26:41,800 --> 00:26:43,880
If they don't agree, then we...

506
00:26:44,280 --> 00:26:45,760
They'd definitely get dragged down.

507
00:26:46,480 --> 00:26:47,920
Doing this once in a while is fine.

508
00:26:47,920 --> 00:26:48,520
But at this rate,

509
00:26:48,520 --> 00:26:49,600
keeping it up for ten days or two weeks,

510
00:26:49,800 --> 00:26:51,320
