511
00:26:51,680 --> 00:26:52,400
Am I right?

512
00:26:52,400 --> 00:26:53,560
All right, all right, all right.

513
00:26:53,560 --> 00:26:54,600
Everyone, ease off a bit.

514
00:26:54,600 --> 00:26:55,440
You're anxious,

515
00:26:55,720 --> 00:26:57,000
but Master Xuan is even more anxious.

516
00:26:57,520 --> 00:26:59,080
