517
00:26:59,080 --> 00:27:00,760
to find a solution for all of you.

518
00:27:01,320 --> 00:27:03,200
Let's not waste any more time.

519
00:27:03,320 --> 00:27:05,120
Let's get started with practice, okay?

520
00:27:05,560 --> 00:27:06,320
Fine.

521
00:27:07,000 --> 00:27:08,760
Director Xuan, Engineer Man, President Jiang.

522
00:27:08,760 --> 00:27:09,480
