523
00:27:09,480 --> 00:27:11,320
You don't have to give me a clear answer,

524
00:27:11,320 --> 00:27:14,000
but I'll make my crew's position clear.

525
00:27:14,400 --> 00:27:15,240
How about this?

526
00:27:15,600 --> 00:27:17,240
Tomorrow, the next day, Sunday's off.

527
00:27:17,280 --> 00:27:18,080
I won't take it off.

528
00:27:18,080 --> 00:27:20,200
I'll bring my crew in for overtime.

529
00:27:20,280 --> 00:27:22,080
