542
00:27:46,240 --> 00:27:46,720
Old Jia.

543
00:27:47,200 --> 00:27:48,000
Everyone, rest assured.

544
00:27:48,280 --> 00:27:50,160
Engineer Man's word always holds.

545
00:27:50,520 --> 00:27:51,800
Two days means two days.

546
00:27:51,960 --> 00:27:53,640
Let's get today's work done first.

547
00:27:53,720 --> 00:27:54,560
Let's get moving, okay?

548
00:27:54,800 --> 00:27:55,440
Come on, let's go.

549
00:27:55,440 --> 00:27:57,760
All right, let's work, get to work.

550
00:27:57,760 --> 00:27:59,000
Come on, come on, get to work.

551
00:28:05,920 --> 00:28:07,760
Put your backs into it, everyone. Two days!

552
00:28:08,720 --> 00:28:09,320
Lao Xuan.

553
00:28:11,000 --> 00:28:13,280
If you ask whether we've made progress lately,

554
00:28:13,760 --> 00:28:16,000
